%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTemple%20Or%20Dargah%2C%20No%20Religious%20Structure%20Can%20Obstruct%20Public%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPublic%20safety%20is%20paramount%20and%20any%20religious%20structure%20encroaching%20upon%20a%20road%2C%20water%20bodies%2C%20or%20rail%20tracks%20must%20go%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today.%20The%20court%20stressed%20that%20India%20is%20a%20secular%20country%20and%20its%20directions%20for%20bulldozer%20action%20and%20anti-encroachment%20drives%20will%20be%20for%20all%20citizens%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20religion%20they%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20Justice%20KV%20Viswanathan%20was%20hearing%20petitions%20challenging%20bulldozer%20action%20against%20people%20accused%20of%20crimes.%20The%20trend%2C%20which%20has%20caught%20on%20in%20several%20states%2C%20is%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20'bulldozer%20justice'.%20The%20state%20authorities%20have%20maintained%20that%20only%20illegal%20construction%20is%20demolished%20in%20such%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20appeared%20for%20three%20states%20--%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Asked%20if%20being%20accused%20in%20a%20criminal%20case%20can%20be%20a%20ground%20for%20facing%20bulldozer%20action%2C%20Mr%20Mehta%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20absolutely%20not%2C%20even%20for%20heinous%20crimes%20like%20rape%20or%20terrorism.%20Like%20my%20lord%20said%20it%20cannot%20also%20be%20that%20the%20notice%20issued%20is%20stuck%20one%20day%20before%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20there%20are%20different%20laws%20for%20municipal%20corporations%20and%20panchayats.%20%26quot%3BThere%20should%20also%20be%20an%20online%20portal%20so%20people%20are%20aware%2C%20once%20you%20digitise%20it%20there%20is%20a%20record.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Solicitor%20General%20then%20said%20he%20was%20worried%20that%20the%20court%20was%20issuing%20directions%20based%20on%20a%20few%20instances%20alleging%20that%20one%20community%20was%20being%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20a%20secular%20country%20and%20our%20directions%20will%20be%20for%20all%2C%20irrespective%20of%20religion%20or%20community.%20Of%20course%2C%20for%20encroachment%2C%20we%20have%20said...%20if%20it%20is%20on%20a%20public%20road%2C%20footpath%2C%20water%20body%20or%20railway%20line%20area...%20If%20there%20is%20any%20religious%20structure%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20road%2C%20be%20it%20gurudwara%20or%20dargah%20or%20temple%2C%20it%20cannot%20obstruct%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Gavai%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20unauthorised%20construction%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20one%20law%2C%20it%20is%20not%20dependent%20on%20religion%20or%20faith%20or%20beliefs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Advocate%20Vrinda%20Grover%20appears%20for%20UN%20Rapporteur%20and%20makes%20arguments%20on%20housing%20availability.%20The%20Solicitor%20General%20objected.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20for%20whom%20they%20are%2C%20we%20don't%20want%20this%20to%20internationalise.%20Our%20Constitutional%20courts%20are%20powerful%20enough%20and%20our%20government%20is%20assisting%20non-adversarialy.%20We%20don't%20need%20an%20international%20agency%20to%20come%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Advocate%20CU%20Singh%2C%20appearing%20for%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20said%20his%20only%20point%20was%20that%20bulldozer%20action%20not%20be%20used%20as%20a%20crime-fighting%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mehta%20said%20bulldozer%20action%20against%20minorities%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bfar%20and%20few%20between%26quot%3B.%20The%20bench%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20some%20or%20two%20persons%2C%20the%20figure%20is%204.45%20lakh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727764260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftemple-or-dargah-no-religious-structure-can-obstruct-public-supreme-court-6690087%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Public%20safety%20is%20paramount%20and%20any%20religious%20structure%20encroaching%20upon%20a%20road%2C%20water%20bodies%2C%20or%20rail%20tracks%20must%20go%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftemple-or-dargah-no-religious-structure-can-obstruct-public-supreme-court-6690087%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTies%20Not%20Normal%20With%20China%2C%20Want%20Pre-2020%20Situation%20On%20Ground%26quot%3B%3A%20Army%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20with%20China%20is%20%26quot%3Bstable%20but%20not%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Indian%20Army%20Chief%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi.%20Speaking%20at%20the%20Chanakya%20Defence%20Dialogue%2C%20Gen%20Dwivedi%20said%20the%20current%20state%20of%20affairs%20remains%20%26quot%3Bsensitive%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20India%20is%20fully%20prepared%20for%20any%20contingency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Dwivedi%20explained%20that%20India%20aims%20to%20restore%20the%20situation%20to%20its%20pre-2020%20status%2C%20prior%20to%20the%20military%20standoff%20that%20began%20in%20May%202020.%20This%20would%20involve%20returning%20to%20the%20conditions%20that%20existed%20in%20terms%20of%20ground%20occupation%2C%20buffer%20zones%2C%20and%20patrols.%20He%20said%20that%20until%20this%20restoration%20is%20achieved%2C%20the%20situation%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20sensitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20is%20stable%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20normal%20and%20it's%20sensitive.%20If%20that%20be%20the%20case%20what%20are%20we%20wanting%3F%20We%20want%20that%20the%20situation%20that%20was%20there%20pre-April%202020%20should%20be%20restored%2C%26quot%3B%20General%20Dwivedi%20said.%20%26quot%3BWith%20China%2C%20you%20must%20compete%2C%20cooperate%2C%20coexist%2C%20confront%2C%20and%20contest.%20So%20until%20that%20situation%20is%20restored%2C%20as%20far%20as%20we%20are%20concerned%2C%20the%20situation%20will%20remain%20sensitive%20and%20we%20are%20fully%20operationally%20prepared%20to%20face%20any%20kind%20of%20contingency.%20Trust%20has%20become%20the%20biggest%20casualty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Dwivedi%20said%20that%20despite%20ongoing%20diplomatic%20talks%2C%20the%20execution%20of%20any%20agreements%20depends%20on%20military%20commanders%20on%20the%20ground.%20Although%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bpositive%20signalling%26quot%3B%20from%20diplomatic%20talks%2C%20full%20disengagement%20has%20not%20been%20accomplished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20positive%20signalling%20is%20coming%20from%20the%20diplomatic%20side%2C%20but%20what%20we%20need%20to%20understand%20(is%20that)%20the%20diplomatic%20side%20gives%20options%20and%20possibilities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20But%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20execution%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20when%20it%20relates%20to%20ground%20per%20se%3B%20it%20is%20dependent%20on%20the%20military%20commanders%20on%20both%20sides%20to%20take%20those%20decisions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClashes%20between%20India%20and%20China%20began%20in%20Ladakh's%20Galwan%20Valley%20in%20June%202020%20marking%20a%20turning%20point%20and%20deteriorating%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20Despite%2021%20rounds%20of%20Corps%20Commander-level%20talks%2C%20critical%20friction%20points%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20such%20as%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%2C%20remain%20unresolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727764200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-06%2F8d20anpg_ladakh-genericpixabay_650x400_17_June_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndt