%20Rao-directed%20movie%20--%20to%20shine%20the%20spotlight%20on%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20government%20performance%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20women's%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPosters%20put%20up%20across%20the%20state%20have%20'Laapataa%20Ladies'%20written%20on%20them%20along%20with%20a%20short%20sentence%20in%20Marathi%3A%20%26quot%3B64%2C000%20women%20missing%20in%20a%20year.%26quot%3B%20They%20also%20have%20silhouettes%20resembling%20Chief%20Minister%20Shinde%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movie%2C%20Laapataa%20Ladies%2C%20released%20last%20year%20and%20garnered%20rave%20reviews%20for%20its%20message%20against%20patriarchy%20delivered%20through%20the%20comedy-drama%20genre.%20It%20has%20been%20chosen%20as%20India's%20official%20entry%20to%20the%20Oscars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20campaign%20also%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20sexual%20abuse%20of%20two%20schoolgirls%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Badlapur%20last%20month.%20It%20specifically%20targets%20Mr%20Fadnavis%2C%20who%20handles%20the%20Home%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20Assembly%20in%20August%20last%20year%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20women%20who%20go%20missing%20in%20the%20state%20don't%20return%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen's%20safety%20is%20a%20cause%20of%20concern%20for%20the%20country.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20around%2064%2C000%20girls%20and%20women%20go%20missing%20every%20year%20and%20during%20Covid%20in%202019%20and%202020%20the%20number%20was%20the%20same.%20In%202021%2C%2061%2C000%20cases%20were%20registered.%2087%25%20of%20them%20have%20returned%20home%2C%20while%20in%202022%2C%2086%25%20of%20the%20missing%20girls%20and%20women%20have%20returned.%20We%20have%20been%20taking%20steps%20to%20bring%20this%20percentage%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20now%20cited%20the%20same%20number%20to%20target%20the%20Mahayuti%20government%20on%20its%20track%20record%20on%20women's%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20reach%20out%20to%20women%20voters%20ahead%20of%20the%20election%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20announced%20the%20'Majhi%20Ladki%20Bahin%20Yojana'%2C%20under%20which%20eligible%20women%20in%20the%2021-65%20years%20age%20group%20will%20receive%20Rs%201%2C500%20per%20month%20if%20their%20family%20income%20is%20less%20than%20Rs%202.5%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20election%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20tough%20fight%20for%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20of%20BJP%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20NCP%20faction%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar.%20The%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20bloc%20of%20Congress%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20and%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20faction%20are%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20In%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20four%20months%20back%2C%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20had%20put%20up%20a%20stellar%20show%2C%20winning%2030%20out%20of%20the%20state's%2048%20seats.%20While%20it%20will%20be%20looking%20to%20build%20on%20its%20poll%20success%2C%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20will%20try%20to%20turn%20the%20tables%20in%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727754600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fiomvnod_laapataa-ladies-congress_625x300_01_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-launches-laapataa-ladies-campaign-ahead-of-maharashtra-election-6689272%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Maharashtra%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20launched%20a%20'Laapataa%20Ladies'%20campaign%20--%20named%20after%20the%20Kiran%20Rao-directed%20movie%20--%20to%20shine%20the%20spotlight%20on%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20government%20performance%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20women's%20safety.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-launches-laapataa-ladies-campaign-ahead