%20Act%20at%20an%20earlier%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lacey%20Act%20prohibits%20interstate%20trade%20in%20certain%20wildlife%20and%20is%20used%20by%20authorities%20to%20combat%20wildlife%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20his%20prison%20sentence%2C%20Schubarth%20was%20ordered%20to%20pay%20a%20%2420%2C000%20fine%20to%20the%20Lacey%20Act%20Reward%20Fund%2C%20a%20%244%2C000%20payment%20to%20the%20National%20Fish%20and%20Wildlife%20Foundation%20and%20a%20%24200%20special%20assessment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727747400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fekobrb7g_arthur-schubarth_625x300_01_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-man-imports-genetic-material-to-create-enormous-hybrid-sheep-arrested-6688770%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20who%20tried%20to%20breed%20enormous%20hybrid%20sheep%20using%20genetic%20material%20from%20endangered%20animals%20so%20he%20could%20sell%20them%20to%20trophy%20hunting%20ranches%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%20six%20months%20in%20prison%2C%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20said%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-man-imports-genetic-material-to-create-enormous-hybrid-sheep-arrested-6688770%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20'mastermind'%20behind%20India's%20biggest%20jailbreak%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727747333000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3c7d%2Flive%2F31a9f010-169a-11ef-9b16-15114b27fe47.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1dd9rj3vmyo%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nearly%202