%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fcould-constitute-career-suicide-shazam-star-zachary-levi-endorses-trump-for-president%2Farticleshow%2F113832238.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113832238.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EZachary%20Levi%2C%20known%20for%20his%20role%20as%20Shazam%2C%20endorsed%20Donald%20Trump%20during%20a%20political%20event%20with%20Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr%20and%20Tulsi%20Gabbard%20in%20Michigan.%20Raised%20in%20a%20conservative%20family%2C%20Levi%20highlighted%20his%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20current%20political%20system.%20He%20acknowledged%20potential%20career%20risks%20in%20Hollywood%20but%20stated%20his%20endorsement%20aligns%20with%20his%20values%2C%20garnering%20support%20from%20fans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fcould-constitute-career-suicide-shazam-star-zachary-levi-endorses-trump-for-president%2Farticleshow%2F113832238.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fcould-constitute-career-suicide-shazam-star-zachary-levi-endorses-trump-for-president%2Famp_articleshow%2F113832238.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fcould-constitute-career-suicide-shazam-star-zachary-levi-endorses-trump-for-president%2Famp_articleshow%2F113832238.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gavaskar%20Not%20Happy%20With%20India's%20Tactic%20vs%20BAN%2C%20Says%20%26quot%3BMan%20With%209000%20Runs...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20on%20Monday%20put%20up%20a%20terrific%20batting%20display%20on%20the%20fourth%20day%20of%20the%20second%20Test%20against%20Bangladesh%20at%20Green%20Park%20stadium%20in%20Kanpur.%20With%20the%20second%20and%20third%20day%20of%20play%20getting%20completely%20washed%20out%20due%20to%20rain%2C%20India%20needed%20an%20out-of-the-box%20performance%20to%20take%20the%20game%20to%20a%20point%20that%20it%20could%20yield%20a%20result.%20The%20hosts%20first%20bundled%20out%20Bangladesh%20at%20the%20score%20of%20233%20and%20then%20boasted%20of%20a%20powerful%20batting%20attack.%20The%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20side%20posted%20285%20for%209%20in%2034.4%20overs%20and%20then%20declared%20the%20innings%20with%20a%20lead%20of%2052%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEn%20route%20to%20the%20massive%20effort%2C%20India%20registered%20the%20fastest%2050%2C%20100%2C%20150%2C%20200%2C%20and%20250%20runs%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Test%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20did%20a%20fantastic%20job%20on%20the%20day%2C%20former%20captain%20and%20now%20a%20commentator%2C%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%2C%20was%20unhappy%20with%20the%20batting%20line-up%20of%20the%20side.%20He%20expressed%20his%20opinions%20on%20JioCinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20India%20lost%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20as%20the%20second%20wicket%20in%20the%20innings%2C%20everyone%20was%20waiting%20to%20see%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20who%20bats%20at%20the%20number%20four%20position%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20To%20everyone's%20surprise%2C%20India%20sent%20Rishabh%20Pant%20and%20held%20back%20Kohli%2C%20only%20to%20send%20him%20later%20at%20fifth%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20talking%20about%20a%20man%20who%20got%20almost%209%2C000%20runs%20in%20Test%20cricket%20batting%20at%20No.%204%2C%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0said%20Gavaskar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pant%20fell%20for%20an%2011-ball%209%2C%20Kohli%20scored%2047%20runs%20off%2035%20balls%20with%20the%20help%20of%20four%20fours%20and%20one%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBatting%20maestro%20Virat%20Kohli%20on%20Monday%20registered%20yet%20another%20world%20record%20to%20his%20name.%20This%20time%2C%20he%20has%20surpassed%20the%20legendary%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20to%20reach%20the%20milestone.%20Kohli%20became%20the%20fastest%20player%20to%20score%2027%2C000%20international%20runs.%20Kohli%20achieved%20it%20in%20594th%20innings%2C%20surpassing%20Sachin%20Tendulkar's%20previous%20record%20(623%20innings).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20Sangakkara%20(648%20innings)%20and%20Ricky%20Ponting%20(650%20innings)%20are%20the%20only%20other%20players%20to%20hit%2027000%20international%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20stumps%20on%20Day%204%20vs%20Bangladesh%20in%20Kanpur%2C%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20struck%20twice%20to%20reduce%20the%20guests%20to%2026%20for%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727746680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fnepmpbpg_sunil-gavaskar-bcci_625x300_05_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-bangladesh-2024%2Fsunil-gavaskar-not-happy-with-indias-tactic-vs-bangladesh-says-man-with-9000-runs-6686328%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20India%20did%20a%20fantastic%20job%20on%20Day%204%20of%20second%20Test%20vs%20Bangladesh%2C%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20was%20unhappy%20with%20the%20batting%20strategy%20of%20the%20side.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-bangladesh-2024%2Fsunil-gavaskar-not-happy-with-indias-tactic-vs-bangladesh-says-man-with-9000-runs-6686328%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20conducting%20'limited%2C%20localised%20and%20targeted%20raids'%20inside%20Lebanon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727746440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F10%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-israel-lebanon-hezbollah_6702221.jpg%3F20241001022116%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisrael-hezbollah-operation-northern-arrows-based-on-precise-intelligence-israeli-military-13225621%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel's%20military%20forces%20have%20crossed%20the%20border%20into