%3ETo%20qualify%20for%20an%20apartment%2C%20each%20household%20must%20meet%20specific%20income%20requirements.%20These%20vary%20across%20developments%20depending%20on%20unit%20size%20and%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApplying%20for%20the%20housing%20lottery%20is%20free%2C%20but%20competition%20is%20stiff%3A%20According%20to%20the%20HPD%2C%20on%20average%2C%20there%20are%20450%20applications%20received%20per%20rental%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mitchell%20received%20the%20offer%20for%20a%20one-bedroom%20lottery%20apartment%20in%20June%20last%20year%2C%20it%20was%20perfect%20timing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20been%20living%20in%20a%20studio%20apartment%20in%20Brooklyn%20for%20about%20a%20year%20and%20had%20just%20renewed%20her%20lease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20had%20just%20raised%20my%20rent%2C%20and%20I%20had%20locked%20it%20in%20for%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Mitchell%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20price%20of%20that%20studio%20apartment%20on%20the%20second%20floor%20would've%20been%20%2420%20more%20than%20this%20lottery%20apartment%20on%20the%20seventh%20floor%20with%20a%20one%20bedroom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221867%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20sitting%20at%20her%20work%20desk%20in%20her%20apartment.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66dfb30ea0ff598b266605c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShe%20says%20it%20took%20about%20two%20years%20for%20her%20to%20hear%20back%20regarding%20her%20lottery%20apartment%20application.%3Cp%3EMolly%20Stromoski%20for%20NYC%20Department%20of%20Housing%20Preservation%20and%20Development%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20decided%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20lottery%20apartment%2C%20and%20thankfully%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20break%20her%20previous%20lease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20like%2C%20'Sure.%20As%20long%20as%20you%20can%20be%20out%20by%20August%2030%20%E2%8