ential%20to%20reach%20more%20than%20200%20million%20viewers%2C%20which%20is%20Prime%20Video's%20monthly%20reach%2C%20according%20to%20Amazon's%20most%20recent%20public%20disclosure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20goes%20well%2C%20Amazon%20could%20repeat%20the%20approach%20with%20other%20big%20news%20events%2C%20one%20of%20the%20people%20close%20to%20the%20deal%20talks%20said.%20Those%20events%20could%20include%20the%20presidential%20inauguration%20or%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20address%2C%20this%20person%20predicted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20toe%20in%20the%20water%20for%20them%20in%20that%20they're%20trying%20to%20get%20beyond%20sports%20to%20other%2C%20seasonal%20special%20types%20of%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20person%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20news-adjacent%20programming%20they%20could%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20people%20close%20to%20the%20deal%20talks%20said%20the%20election-night%20special%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20ad-free.%20No%20final%20decisions%20have%20been%20made%2C%20though.%20But%20Amazon%20and%20other%20tech-rooted%20streamers%20have%20seen%20how%20live%20programming%2C%20like%20comedy%20specials%20and%20awards%20shows%2C%20creates%20appointment%20viewing%20that%20can%20be%20highly%20attractive%20to%20advertisers.%20Advertisers%2C%20and%20especially%20marketers%20with%20time-sensitive%20product%20launches%2C%20have%20shown%20a%20willingness%20to%20pay%20high%20prices%20to%20reach%20large%20live%20audiences.%20Amazon%20this%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-prime-video-ads-early-success-with-advertisers-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturned%20on%20ads%20in%20Prime%20Video%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20gunning%20for%20the%20nearly%20%2470%20billion%20in%20annual%20TV%20ad%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Amazon%2C%20specifically%2C%20filmed%20entertainment%20and%20sports%20programming%20%E2%80%94%20part%20of%20Prime%20Video%20%E2%80%94%20also%20serves%20to%20keep%20people%20subscribing%20to%20its%20lucrative%20Prime%20service%20and%20get%20people%20to%20shop%20more%20on%20the%20platform.%20Prime%20Video's%202023%20Black%20Friday%20NFL%20game%2C%20for%20example%2C%20showed%20QR%20codes%20during%20breaks%20to%20promote%20deals%20on%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20fits%20in%20with%20their%20interest%20in%20disruptions%20and%20amassing%20big%20audiences%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20second%20person%20close%20to%20the%20deal%20talks%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20be%20in%20the%20big-event%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f7a9c20-5ffc-43f3-a0df-b0f758efb495%5C%22%3ENews%20has%20been%20slow%20to%20shift%20to%20streaming%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20champions%20of%20the%20election-night%20special%20within%20Amazon%20include%20Mike%20Hopkins%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20Prime%20Video%20and%20Amazon%20MGM%20Studios%2C%20and%20his%20powerful%20No.%202%2C%20Albert%20Cheng%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20Prime%20Video%20US.%20Hopkins%20has%20played%20a%20role%20in%20Prime%20Video's%20aggressive%20expansion%20into%20sports%2C%20which%20has%20created%20tension%20with%20some%20on%20the%20entertainment%20side%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjay-marine-leading-amazon-sports-ambitions-nba-rights-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esee%20the%20sports%20investment%20coming%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20film%20and%20TV%20budgets%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20deal%20goes%20through%2C%20the%20special%20would%20be%20produced%20by%20Jonathan%20Wald%2C%20a%20veteran%20TV%20news%20producer%20who%20executive-produced%20Williams'%20%26quot%3B11th%20Hour%26quot%3B%20on%20MSNBC%20and%20has%20lately%20focused%20on%20new%20news%20formats.%20He%20helped%20Don%20Lemon%20launch%20shows%20on%20social%20media%2C%20for%20example.%20Williams'%20reps%20at%20talent%20agency%20CAA%20have%20also%20been%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20entertainment%20and%20sports%20have%20shifted%20to%20streaming%2C%20news%20has%20been%20slower%20to%20follow.%20Legacy%20broadcasters%20like%20NBC%20News%20and%20ABC%20News%20have%20invested%20in%20live-streamed%20content%3B%20CNN%20has%20planned%20a%20streaming%20subscription%20service%2C%20but%20it's%20had%20starts%20and%20stops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20companies%20with%20streaming%20services%20have%20generally%20steered%20clear%20of%20news%20%E2%80%94%20not%20surprisingly%2C%20given%20the%20high%20cost%20of%20operating%20a%20newsroom%20and%20how%20polarizing%20news%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-ceo-ted-sarandos-ads-sports-originals-change-mind-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%20co-CEO%20Ted%20Sarandos%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20rejected%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20streamer%20covering%20breaking%20news.%20Apple%20TV%2B%20drifted%20into%20news-adjacent%20programming%20in%202020%20with%20Jon%20Stewart%2C%20who%20hosted%20a%20weekly%20comedy%20news%20show.%20But%20Stewart%20walked%20away%20after%20two%20seasons%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theringer.com%2F2024%2F6%2F13%2F24177435%2Fjon-stewart-talks-apple-split-corporate-constraints-media-regression%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaying%3C%2Fa%3E%20Apple%20increasingly%20wanted%20more%20oversight%20of%20the%20show's%20editorial%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20wants%20to%20bring%20a%20down-the-middle%20presentation%20of%20election%20results%20hosted%20by%20Williams%20with%20a%20lineup%20of%20exclusive%20contributors.%20To%20lend%20a%20nonpartisan%20feel%2C%20the%20plan%20is%20that%20the%20presenters%20won't%20call%20the%20race%20and%20will%20point%20viewers%20to%20third-party%20content%20(which%20could%20include%20sites%20like%20CNN%20and%20NBC%20News%20that%20are%20available%20through%20Amazon%20Channels).%20The%20event%20would%20be%20broadcast%20from%20LA%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20run%20late%20into%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20some%20elements%20would%20be%20familiar%20to%20a%20news%20audience%2C%20Amazon%20is%20expected%20to%20put%20its%20own%20twist%20on%20the%20potential%20presentation%2C%20similar%20to%20how%20it%20souped%20up%20the%20production%20of%20%26quot%3BThursday%20Night%20Football%26quot%3B%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F8%2F24%2F23842818%2Famazon-thursday-night-football-ai-streaming%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon-screen%20overlays%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20predict%20what%20might%20happen%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-brian-williams-deal-tv-news-details-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727732680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fb003475c877a99b61f29f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-brian-williams-deal-tv-news-details-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Brian%20Williams%20is%20close%20to%20a%20deal%20with%20Amazon%20to%20host%20an%20election-night%20special%20that%20could%20mark%20the%20start%20of%20a%20new%20strategy%20for%20Prime%20Video.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmoses%40insider.com%20(Lucia%20Moses)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-brian-williams-deal-tv-news-details-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20tells%20US%20it%20plans%20to%20launch%20limited%20ground%20incursion%20into%20Lebanon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727732129000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fff2a%2Flive%2Fc66d7d70-7f45-11ef-aa7c-8bb5d2c83013.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fczxgyzq7z2ro%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20US%20official%20told%20the%20BBC's%20US%20partner%20CBS%20that%20the%20operation%20could%20start%20as%20soon%20as%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A54%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fczxgyzq7z2ro%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fczxgyzq7z2ro.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fczxgyzq7z2ro.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Eric%20Adams%20has%20the%20SCOTUS%20supermajority%20to%20thank%20as%20he%20challenges%20his%20bribery%20charge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eric%20Adams%20arrives%20in%20court%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f6b720f9f6733e4be035df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENew%20York%20City%20Mayor%20Eric%20Adams%20arrives%20for%20his%20arraignment%20outside%20Manhattan%20Federal%20Court%20on%20Friday%2C%20Sept.%2027%2C%202024%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20New%20York.%3Cp%3EBarry%20Williams%20for%20New%20York%20Daily%20News%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20New%20York%20City%20mayor%20has%20begun%20formally%20challenging%20last%20week's%20bribery%20and%20fraud%20indictment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20arguments%20in%20Monday's%20motion%20to%20dismiss%20amount%20to%20this%3A%20SCOTUS%20lets%20me%20do%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20recent%20Supreme%20Court%20decision%20helps%20Adams%20by%20requiring%20a%20specific%20quid-pro-quo%20to%20prove%20bribery.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20formal%20attack%20on%20last%20week's%20sweeping%20public%20corruption%20indictment%2C%20New%20York%20City%20Mayor%20Eric%20Adams%20takes%20aim%20at%20what%20his%20lawyer%20says%20is%20the%20weakest%20of%20the%20five%20federal%20charges%3A%20bribery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdams'%20argument%3F%20It's%20not%20bribery%20if%20the%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20lets%20you%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20court%20filing%20on%20Monday%2C%20Adams%20attorney%20Alex%20Spiro%20cites%20a%20groundbreaking%20June%20SCOTUS%20decision%20as%20reason%20enough%20to%20toss%20the%20bribery%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20is%20Snyder%20v.%20United%20States.%20It%20says%20handing%20a%20politician%20a%20bag%20of%20money%20is%20essentially%20A-OK%20under%20federal%20law%2C%20so%20long%20as%20there%20is%20no%20specifically%20stated%20quid-pro-quo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Adams'%20case%2C%20the%20Turkish%20officials%20who%20gave%20him%20%24100%2C000%20in%20upgraded%20flights%20and%20luxurious%20hotel%20stays%20never%20specifically%20linked%20those%20perks%20to%20a%20specific%20request%20for%20something%20in%20return%2C%20Spiro%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20these%20were%20gratuities%2C%20not%20bribes%2C%20the%20lawyer%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%20after%20the%20motion%20was%20filed%2C%20Spiro%20compared%20Adams'%20%24100%2C000%20in%20flights%20and%20accommodations%20to%20perks%20like%20a%20hotel%20room%20upgrade%20or%20a%20good%20table%20at%20a%20restaurant%2C%20which%20are%20regularly%20extended%20to%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20indictment%20does%20not%20sufficiently%20allege%20that%20Adams%20agreed%20to%20accept%20benefits%20in%20exchange%20for%20performing%20an%20official%20act%2C%26quot%3B%20Spiro%20wrote%20in%20Monday's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25178330-us-v-adams-mol-dismissal-20240930%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E25-page%20motion%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20first%20time%20Snyder%20%E2%80%94%20a%20case%20named%20for%20an%20Indiana%20mayor%20who%20took%20%2413%2C000%20from%20a%20truck%20company%20%E2%80%94%20is%20being%20cited%20as%20a%20defense%20in%20a%20major%20public%20corruption%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20makes%20perfect%20sense%20for%20Adams%20to%20cite%20it%2C%20said%20Michel%20Paradis%2C%20an%20attorney%20who%20teaches%20national%20security%20and%20constitutional%20law%20at%20Columbia%20Law%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSnyder%20will%20be%20helpful%20to%20Adams%20principally%20in%20really%20putting%20the%20government%20to%20its%20proof%20on%20the%20quid-pro-quo%20elements%20of%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20Paradis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20prosecutors%20say%20Adams%20enjoyed%20nearly%20a%20decade%20of%20globe-circling%20Turkish%20Airlines%20trips.%20They%20say%20that%20in%20return%2C%20Turkish%20officials%20asked%20for%20a%20few%20small%20favors%20from%20Adams%2C%20including%20that%20he%20not%20mention%20the%20Armenian%20genocide%2C%20and%20that%20he%20sever%20ties%20with%20a%20particular%20community%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20say%20Turkey%20asked%20Adams%20for%20a%20large%20favor%2C%20one%20that%20Adams%20granted%3A%20in%202021%2C%20the%20then-leading%20mayoral%20candidate%20leaned%20on%20city%20fire%20officials%20to%20bend%20the%20rules%20and%20approve%20occupancy%20for%20a%20Midtown%20skyscraper%20that%20held%20the%20Turkish%20consulate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20quotes%20an%20unnamed%20Turkish%20official%20telling%20an%20Adams%20staffer%20that%20because%20Turkey%20had%20supported%20the%20soon-to-be%20mayor%2C%20it%20was%20now%20%26quot%3Bhis%20turn%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20Adams'%20%E2%80%94%20to%20support%20Turkey%20by%20getting%20the%20consulate%20opened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20feds%20say%20Adams%20responded%20when%20told%20by%20the%20staffer%20that%20Turkey%20saw%20this%20as%20%26quot%3Bhis%20turn%26quot%3B%20to%20reciprocate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpiro%20says%20in%20his%20filing%20that%20the%20travel%20perks%20Adams%20enjoyed%20are%20the%20kind%20of%20gifts%20that%20constituents%20or%20foreign%20dignitaries%20routinely%20give%2C%20to%20show%20their%20appreciation%20or%20gain%20access%20to%20a%20politician.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESnyder%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20majority%20opinion%20written%20by%20Justice%20Brett%20Kavanaugh%20and%20joined%20by%20the%20current%20conservative%20supermajority's%20five%20other%20justices%20%E2%80%94%20broadens%20the%20definition%20of%20%26quot%3Bgratuities%26quot%3B%20and%20limits%20the%20definition%20of%20%26quot%3Bbribes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(In%20addition%20to%20Spiro%2C%20Adams%20is%20represented%20by%20Avi%20Perry%20and%20William%20Burck.%20Burck%20is%20on%20the%20board%20of%20Fox%20Corp%2C%20clerked%20for%20Anthony%20Kennedy%2C%20and%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fwilliam-burck.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20a%20friend%20of%20Kavanaugh.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20new%2C%20post-Snyder%20world%2C%20the%20feds%20must%20prove%20that%20a%20politician%20clearly%20knew%20that%20cash%20or%20goods%20are%20being%20offered%20as%20payment%20for%20an%20official%20act%2C%20and%20that%20the%20official%20act%20was%20taken%20specifically%20in%20response%20to%20that%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20the%20SCOTUS%20ruling%20feared%20it%20would%20open%20the%20door%20to%20politicians%20freely%20taking%20handouts.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdams%20will%20argue%20that%20the%20Turkish%20government%20gave%20him%20things%20out%20of%20gratitude%20for%20his%20past%20friendliness%20toward%20Turkey's%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20merely%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bthank%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Paradis%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20government%20will%20argue%20that%20Turkey%20gave%20him%20goodies%2C%20and%20he%20accepted%20those%20goodies%2C%20on%20the%20understanding%20that%20he%20would%20continue%20to%20use%20his%20political%20position%20for%20Turkey's%20benefit%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20constitutional%20law%20expert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrior%20to%20Snyder%2C%20the%20government%20would%20not%20have%20had%20to%20show%20such%20a%20tight%20connection%20between%20the%20bribes%20and%20the%20expectation%20that%20Adams%20would%20do%20things%20for%20them%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Paradis%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20they%20do%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20indictment%20puts%20a%20lot%20of%20emphasis%20on%20the%20consulate%20and%20the%20Armenian%20genocide%20allegations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFederal%20prosecutors%20have%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20motion%20to%20dismiss.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Justice%20Department%20and%20Spiro%20didn't%20immediately%20return%20requests%20for%20comment%20for%20this%20story%20Monday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdams%20has%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20to%20the%20indictment%2C%20which%20also%20charges%20him%20with%20illegally%20accepting%20campaign%20contributions%20from%20Turkish%20officials%20and%20others%20via%20straw%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20convicted%20on%20all%20counts%2C%20he%20faces%20a%20maximum%20of%2045%20years%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-adams-scotus-thank-challenges-bribery-charge-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727731620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fb0e4d75c877a99b61fb39%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-adams-scotus-thank-challenges-bribery-charge-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20June%20decision%20that%20helped%20an%20Indiana%20mayor%20beat%20a%20bribery%20rap%20now%20helps%20Adams%20by%20requiring%20federal%20prosecutors%20prove%20a%20specific%20quid-pro-quo.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22litaliano%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Italiano)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-adams-scotus-thank-challenges-bribery-charge-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%