e%20has%20increased%20by%20over%20300%20percent%20in%20the%20past%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Global%20Burden%20of%20Disease%20Study%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341755%2Fcongenital-heart-disease-in-babies-treatment-surgery-provided-by-hans-foundation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20leading%20cause%20of%20fatality%20among%20Indian%20women%2C%20accounting%20for%20over%2017%20percent%20of%20deaths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20alarming%20statistic%20underscores%20the%20importance%20of%20recognising%20the%20unique%20ways%20heart%20diseases%20manifest%20in%20women%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20awareness%20and%20proactive%20health%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHeart%20disease%20is%20the%20biggest%20killer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeart%20disease%20refers%20to%20a%20range%20of%20conditions%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336492%2Fgoan-artist-xavier-fernandes-makes-christmas-cribs-from-driftwood%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoronary%20artery%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20congenital%20heart%20disease%2C%20arrhythmia%20(irregular%20heartbeats)%2C%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%20and%20more.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20causes%20of%20death%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20heart%20diseases%20are%20preventable%20and%20can%20be%20successfully%20treated%20if%20diagnosed%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20traditional%20belief%20is%20that%20heart%20diseases%20generally%20affect%20women%2010%20years%20later%20than%20men%2C%20this%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20case.%20Just%20like%20younger%20men%20are%20getting%20heart%20attacks%2C%20so%20are%20women%2C%20but%20they%20are%20often%20unaware%20of%20the%20signs%20and%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv